hackern3ws
==========

An alternative front-end for Hacker News.

Dependencies
------------

- CURL
- Memcached (optional)

Configuration
-------------

Every configuration should be tied to the file config.php

Memcached is enabled by default, set MEMCACHED to false to
disable.

Powering up server
------------------

I use PHP's built-in server:

    ./serve.sh -h
